Text.SourceString: Oh, you're the land-dweller, right? Yeah, I remember you.
Text.LocalizedString: Oh, you're the land-dweller, right? Yeah, I remember you.

Text.SourceString: Not bad handling those slimes back there. You've earned a bit of respect from me, that's for sure.
Text.LocalizedString: Not bad handling those slimes back there. You've earned a bit of respect from me, that's for sure.

Text.SourceString: I'm not much for chit-chat. I prefer to keep my eyes open and really see what's going on around me.//<portrait=normal>I hope you don't mind.
Text.LocalizedString: I'm not much for chit-chat. I prefer to keep my eyes open and really see what's going on around me.//<portrait=normal>I hope you don't mind.

Text.SourceString: You're still here, huh?
Text.LocalizedString: You're still here, huh?

Text.SourceString: The safety of our realm is my top priority. I'm here to serve and protect – it's as simple as that.
Text.LocalizedString: The safety of our realm is my top priority. I'm here to serve and protect – it's as simple as that.

Text.SourceString: After last night's patrol, I spent hours just staring at the sea stars, thinking. They really helped me sort out my thoughts.
Text.LocalizedString: After last night's patrol, I spent hours just staring at the sea stars, thinking. They really helped me sort out my thoughts.

Text.SourceString: Sometimes, I catch myself lost in thought about the smallest things. Like today, I was pondering how light dances on the water’s surface and what that says about perspective.//<portrait=annoyed>It gets kinda tiring, to be honest.
Text.LocalizedString: Sometimes, I catch myself lost in thought about the smallest things. Like today, I was pondering how light dances on the water’s surface and what that says about perspective.//<portrait=annoyed>It gets kinda tiring, to be honest.

Text.SourceString: Last night, I couldn't sleep. I ended up reflecting on some old memories and how they've shaped me.//<portrait=normal>It's interesting what you can learn about yourself in those quiet moments.
Text.LocalizedString: Last night, I couldn't sleep. I ended up reflecting on some old memories and how they've shaped me.//<portrait=normal>It's interesting what you can learn about yourself in those quiet moments.

Text.SourceString: Been in some real scrapes, but I always remind myself: stay cool, stay alive. It’s worked so far.
Text.LocalizedString: Been in some real scrapes, but I always remind myself: stay cool, stay alive. It’s worked so far.

Text.SourceString: Rough currents? Sure, I've had my share.//<portrait=annoyed>Being number two in safety isn't easy. I love my job, but it does come with its territory. Things do get crazy around here.
Text.LocalizedString: Rough currents? Sure, I've had my share.//<portrait=annoyed>Being number two in safety isn't easy. I love my job, but it does come with its territory. Things do get crazy around here.

Text.SourceString: Just take a deep breath and focus. Can't let chaos throw you off.
Text.LocalizedString: Just take a deep breath and focus. Can't let chaos throw you off.

Text.SourceString: Me and my trident are practically inseparable. I've trained so much with it, it's practically part of me now.
Text.LocalizedString: Me and my trident are practically inseparable. I've trained so much with it, it's practically part of me now.

Text.SourceString: The king, may his reign continue long, presented me with this trident when I was appointed second in command.//<portrait=happy>It's crafted from royal silver, much like <NPCName>Semeru</>'s, I believe.
Text.LocalizedString: The king, may his reign continue long, presented me with this trident when I was appointed second in command.//<portrait=happy>It's crafted from royal silver, much like <NPCName>Semeru</>'s, I believe.

Text.SourceString: In my line of work, you've always got to think ahead. Anticipate. It's all about strategy.
Text.LocalizedString: In my line of work, you've always got to think ahead. Anticipate. It's all about strategy.

Text.SourceString: In the water, my goal is to blend in, to be unseen.
Text.LocalizedString: In the water, my goal is to blend in, to be unseen.

Text.SourceString: Here's a piece of advice from my mentor: merge with the shadows. For a guard, that's key.//And believe me, it was the toughest training I've ever undergone.
Text.LocalizedString: Here's a piece of advice from my mentor: merge with the shadows. For a guard, that's key.//And believe me, it was the toughest training I've ever undergone.

Text.SourceString: Gliding through water without a sound – it's kind of my specialty. They don't call me the ghost for no reason.//<portrait=happy>Just kidding, nobody actually calls me the ghost. I was just teasing.
Text.LocalizedString: Gliding through water without a sound – it's kind of my specialty. They don't call me the ghost for no reason.//<portrait=happy>Just kidding, nobody actually calls me the ghost. I was just teasing.

Text.SourceString: This Golden Kelp hairpiece? Yeah, it's not standard-issue guard gear.//<portrait=happy>Picked it up myself. Adds a bit of shine to the uniform, don't you think?
Text.LocalizedString: This Golden Kelp hairpiece? Yeah, it's not standard-issue guard gear.//<portrait=happy>Picked it up myself. Adds a bit of shine to the uniform, don't you think?

Text.SourceString: I'm quick enough as it is, so I don't really need a helmet.
Text.LocalizedString: I'm quick enough as it is, so I don't really need a helmet.

Text.SourceString: This gold plate on my arm has been a real lifesaver in quite a few close calls.//I'm never going without it again.
Text.LocalizedString: This gold plate on my arm has been a real lifesaver in quite a few close calls.//I'm never going without it again.

Text.SourceString: Each of these gold plates has its own story. Like this one, it's been with me since my first patrol. It's more than armor, it's a memory...a shiny memory.
Text.LocalizedString: Each of these gold plates has its own story. Like this one, it's been with me since my first patrol. It's more than armor, it's a memory...a shiny memory.

Text.SourceString: You get used to the early wake-up calls in the barracks.//<portrait=annoyed>It's the sound of discipline...and occasionally someone's snoring.
Text.LocalizedString: You get used to the early wake-up calls in the barracks.//<portrait=annoyed>It's the sound of discipline...and occasionally someone's snoring.

Text.SourceString: The barracks might not be luxurious, but it's home. Plus, there's a sense of camaraderie you can't find anywhere else.
Text.LocalizedString: The barracks might not be luxurious, but it's home. Plus, there's a sense of camaraderie you can't find anywhere else.

Text.SourceString: Well, you know, you're there too.
Text.LocalizedString: Well, you know, you're there too.

Text.SourceString: In the barracks, your squad is your family. We look out for each other, no matter what.
Text.LocalizedString: In the barracks, your squad is your family. We look out for each other, no matter what.

Text.SourceString: Except for when we lost Poseidon, I suppose. That was a sad time.
Text.LocalizedString: Except for when we lost Poseidon, I suppose. That was a sad time.

Text.SourceString: You wouldn't believe the amount of gear maintenance we do daily. But hey, a shiny trident is a happy trident.
Text.LocalizedString: You wouldn't believe the amount of gear maintenance we do daily. But hey, a shiny trident is a happy trident.

Text.SourceString: Afternoon patrols are my favorite. The ocean has a different vibe then, more peaceful.
Text.LocalizedString: Afternoon patrols are my favorite. The ocean has a different vibe then, more peaceful.

Text.SourceString: Before lights out, I like to spend some time alone, just reflecting on the day. Helps me stay grounded.
Text.LocalizedString: Before lights out, I like to spend some time alone, just reflecting on the day. Helps me stay grounded.

Text.SourceString: And, of course, there's always time for a quick swim. It's the perfect way to clear your mind after a busy day.
Text.LocalizedString: And, of course, there's always time for a quick swim. It's the perfect way to clear your mind after a busy day.

Text.SourceString: Watching a storm from underwater is mesmerizing.
Text.LocalizedString: Watching a storm from underwater is mesmerizing.

Text.SourceString: During a heavy rain, the ocean feels different. Can you feel it?
Text.LocalizedString: During a heavy rain, the ocean feels different. Can you feel it?

Text.SourceString: I've always found the rain soothing.
Text.LocalizedString: I've always found the rain soothing.

Text.SourceString: A big storm stirs everything up, but afterwards, the ocean is so clear and peaceful.
Text.LocalizedString: A big storm stirs everything up, but afterwards, the ocean is so clear and peaceful.

Text.SourceString: Winter underwater is quieter. Many creatures migrate or hide away.
Text.LocalizedString: Winter underwater is quieter. Many creatures migrate or hide away.

Text.SourceString: Winter patrols are challenging; the colder water slows everything down, and visibility drops with the early darkness.
Text.LocalizedString: Winter patrols are challenging; the colder water slows everything down, and visibility drops with the early darkness.

Text.SourceString: During Winter, we're extra vigilant. The sea behaves differently – more unpredictable currents and quieter marine life.
Text.LocalizedString: During Winter, we're extra vigilant. The sea behaves differently – more unpredictable currents and quieter marine life.

Text.SourceString: Now that the cold has set in, we need to rely even more on intuition and keen observation.
Text.LocalizedString: Now that the cold has set in, we need to rely even more on intuition and keen observation.

Text.SourceString: In Spring, the water feels different – fresher, clearer. Can you feel it?
Text.LocalizedString: In Spring, the water feels different – fresher, clearer. Can you feel it?

Text.SourceString: The extended daylight in Summer leads to longer patrols. It can be exhausting at times.
Text.LocalizedString: The extended daylight in Summer leads to longer patrols. It can be exhausting at times.

Text.SourceString: Summer poses unique challenges for us guards. The increase in people and activities near the water demands heightened vigilance.//<portrait=annoyed>Those land dwellers can be unpredictable – no offense.
Text.LocalizedString: Summer poses unique challenges for us guards. The increase in people and activities near the water demands heightened vigilance.//<portrait=annoyed>Those land dwellers can be unpredictable – no offense.

Text.SourceString: Yesterday I nearly turned the kitchen into an underwater bonfire. Who knew seaweed could ignite like that?
Text.LocalizedString: Yesterday I nearly turned the kitchen into an underwater bonfire. Who knew seaweed could ignite like that?

Text.SourceString: I tried baking once. The cake was supposed to rise, right?//<portrait=happy>Mine just expanded sideways – ended up with a very wide, very flat 'pancake'.
Text.LocalizedString: I tried baking once. The cake was supposed to rise, right?//<portrait=happy>Mine just expanded sideways – ended up with a very wide, very flat 'pancake'.

Text.SourceString: I'm heading over to Sleepy Eel to grab a bunch of their burgers. They're really tasty, and honestly, it's cheaper than me trying to cook.//<portrait=happy>Plus, there's no guarantee mine would even taste good.
Text.LocalizedString: I'm heading over to Sleepy Eel to grab a bunch of their burgers. They're really tasty, and honestly, it's cheaper than me trying to cook.//<portrait=happy>Plus, there's no guarantee mine would even taste good.

Text.SourceString: Just a reminder: the seaweed forest is dense this season. Make sure your fins are clear of the fronds. Don't want anyone getting tangled.
Text.LocalizedString: Just a reminder: the seaweed forest is dense this season. Make sure your fins are clear of the fronds. Don't want anyone getting tangled.

Text.SourceString: Heads up, <PlayerName>$Player</>. There's been a sighting of a lone shark near the southern cove. Keep your distance and stay alert.//<portrait=annoyed>And no, it's not <NPCName>Semeru</>.
Text.LocalizedString: Heads up, <PlayerName>$Player</>. There's been a sighting of a lone shark near the southern cove. Keep your distance and stay alert.//<portrait=annoyed>And no, it's not <NPCName>Semeru</>.

Text.SourceString: The simulated rescue operation was intense. It's good practice, though – helps us prepare for real emergencies.
Text.LocalizedString: The simulated rescue operation was intense. It's good practice, though – helps us prepare for real emergencies.

Text.SourceString: We had an endurance swim as part of our training. It's exhausting, but it's amazing how much you can push your limits.
Text.LocalizedString: We had an endurance swim as part of our training. It's exhausting, but it's amazing how much you can push your limits.

Text.SourceString: In today's drill, I realized I need to improve my reaction time. It's crucial for those unexpected situations.
Text.LocalizedString: In today's drill, I realized I need to improve my reaction time. It's crucial for those unexpected situations.

Text.SourceString: Spent the morning oiling my trident. Keeping it in good condition is key for it to function properly.
Text.LocalizedString: Spent the morning oiling my trident. Keeping it in good condition is key for it to function properly.

Text.SourceString: Checked my armor for any cracks or wear. It's our first line of defense, so it's important to keep it well-maintained.
Text.LocalizedString: Checked my armor for any cracks or wear. It's our first line of defense, so it's important to keep it well-maintained.

Text.SourceString: Had to repair a strap on my gauntlet today. Can't afford any equipment malfunctions during patrols.
Text.LocalizedString: Had to repair a strap on my gauntlet today. Can't afford any equipment malfunctions during patrols.

Text.SourceString: Noticed a school of mackerel moving differently than usual. Wonder if it's due to the changing ocean currents.
Text.LocalizedString: Noticed a school of mackerel moving differently than usual. Wonder if it's due to the changing ocean currents.

Text.SourceString: The coral seems to be thriving this season. The colors are more vibrant than I've seen in years.
Text.LocalizedString: The coral seems to be thriving this season. The colors are more vibrant than I've seen in years.

Text.SourceString: Had a strategy discussion with <NPCName>Denali</> today. It's always good to get a fresh perspective on patrol routes.
Text.LocalizedString: Had a strategy discussion with <NPCName>Denali</> today. It's always good to get a fresh perspective on patrol routes.

Text.SourceString: The currents are strong today.
Text.LocalizedString: The currents are strong today.

Text.SourceString: Noticed a change in the water temperature this morning. This can't be good.
Text.LocalizedString: Noticed a change in the water temperature this morning. This can't be good.

Text.SourceString: I accidentally scared a school of fish during patrol. They scattered like I was <NPCName>Semeru</> or something. It was quite a sight.
Text.LocalizedString: I accidentally scared a school of fish during patrol. They scattered like I was <NPCName>Semeru</> or something. It was quite a sight.

Text.SourceString: The princess trusts me with her safety, and that's not something I take lightly. Our bond goes beyond duty.
Text.LocalizedString: The princess trusts me with her safety, and that's not something I take lightly. Our bond goes beyond duty.

Text.SourceString: The princess and I, we went to school together. She's more than my charge; she's a dear friend.
Text.LocalizedString: The princess and I, we went to school together. She's more than my charge; she's a dear friend.

Text.SourceString: Once, the princess and I got caught in an unexpected current during a swim. We ended up laughing about it for hours afterward – it turned into quite the adventure!
Text.LocalizedString: Once, the princess and I got caught in an unexpected current during a swim. We ended up laughing about it for hours afterward – it turned into quite the adventure!

Text.SourceString: Oh, and we nearly dodged a huge ship. Talk about a close call!
Text.LocalizedString: Oh, and we nearly dodged a huge ship. Talk about a close call!

Text.SourceString: Back in Atlantoria, the princess and I would often sneak off to explore the hidden gardens. Those were some of our best adventures.
Text.LocalizedString: Back in Atlantoria, the princess and I would often sneak off to explore the hidden gardens. Those were some of our best adventures.

Text.SourceString: There were quiet evenings in Atlantoria when the princess and I would just sit by the water's edge, talking about everything and nothing.//I miss it.
Text.LocalizedString: There were quiet evenings in Atlantoria when the princess and I would just sit by the water's edge, talking about everything and nothing.//I miss it.

Text.SourceString: I recall attending a ball in Atlantoria with the princess.//<portrait=normal>We danced the entire night away and even joined other merfolk in a surface race. We didn't win, but it was still a blast.
Text.LocalizedString: I recall attending a ball in Atlantoria with the princess.//<portrait=normal>We danced the entire night away and even joined other merfolk in a surface race. We didn't win, but it was still a blast.
